He revealed in a tweet that his eldest daughter Khwezi (25) had committed suicide overnight. “My eldest daughter, Khwezi Mthembu, last night committed suicide at our Pelican parliamentary village home in #CapeTown. We are in deep pain. We don’t know what led her to take her own life at such a tender age of 25 years,” said Mthembu. My eldest daughter , Khwezi Mthembu , last night committed suicide at our Pelican parliamentary village home in #Capetown . We are in deep pain . We don’t know what led her to take her own life at such a tender age of 25 years . — Jackson Mthembu (@JacksonMthembu_) March 20, 2019  